metadata.name: Sunset Daydream
metadata.description:
I chase sunsets everywhere I go
Documenting these moments of miracles in the sky
Dreaming of yesterday’s sunset until today’s is here
Hold onto these moments, as they can never be replicated
Every sunset is a 1 / 1, just like you

This photograph was taken on February 14, 2022 in Punta Mita, Mexico.
